#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Show for all documents</guilabel> checkbox can be unchecked to "
"show only the bookmarks from the current document."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filter bar at the top of <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> view can be used "
"to filter the content of bookmark list pane according to the text in the box."
msgstr ""
"Filtririba abil <guilabel>järjehoidja</guilabel>vaate ülaosas saab "
"filtreerida järjehoidjate paneeli loendit vastavalt tekstikasti sisestatule."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list pane permits to view the bookmark list in a tree-like fashion: each "
"document in the list can be <quote>expanded</quote> or <quote>collapsed</"
"quote> by clicking on the <guiicon>&lt;</guiicon> or <guiicon>v</guiicon> "
"icon next to it."
msgstr ""
"Loendipaneel võimaldab näha järjehoidjate loendit puukujulisena ning iga "
"loendi dokumenti saab <quote>laiendada</quote> ehk avada, kui klõpsata selle "
"juures oleval <guiicon>&lt;</guiicon> või <guiicon>v</guiicon> ikoonil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click menu of document item can be used to open document, rename its "
"item or remove it from the list. Remember that the removal of a document "
"item leads to the removal of all bookmarks in the corresponding document."
msgstr ""
"Parema klõpsuga avatava dokumendi kontekstimenüü abil saab avada dokumendi, "
"muuta selle nime või eemaldada selle loendist. Pane tähele, et dokumendi "
"eemaldamine tähendab kõigi vastava dokumendi järjehoidjate eemaldamist."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click menus of individual bookmark items allow you to go to the "
"bookmark, rename or remove it."
msgstr ""
"Konkreetse järjehoidja parema klõpsuga avatava kontekstimenüü abil saab "
"minna järjehoidja kohale, järjehoidja nime muuta või selle eemaldada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Right-click menu of items in the table of contents can be used to create "
"bookmarks or go to the next or previous bookmark."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Options"
msgstr "Käsurea võtmed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Though &okular; may most often be started from the &kde; program menu, or a "
"desktop icon, it can also be opened at the command line prompt of a terminal "
"window. There are a few useful options that are available when doing this."
msgstr ""
"Kuigi enamik käivitab &okular;i tõenäoliselt &kde; rakenduste menüüst või "
"töölaual asuvalt ikoonilt, saab selle avada ka terminaliaknas käsurealt. "
"Viimasel juhul on olemas mõned tulusad võtmed, mida nüüd kirjeldame."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify a File"
msgstr "Faili määramine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By specifying the path and name of a particular file the user can have "
"&okular; open that file immediately upon startup. This option might look "
"something like the following:"
msgstr ""
"Määrates konkreetse faili asukoha ja nime, saab kasutaja lasta &okular;il "
"avada antud faili vahetult käivitamisel. Seda saab teha käsuga, mis võib "
"välja näha näiteks nii:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>okular</command> "
"<option><replaceable>/home/myhome/docs/mydoc.pdf</replaceable></option> </"
"userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>okular</command> "
"<option><replaceable>/home/myhome/docs/mydoc.pdf</replaceable></option> </"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For &PDF; documents, the name can be given as <replaceable>document_name</"
"replaceable>#<replaceable>named_destination</replaceable> where "
"<replaceable>named_destination</replaceable> is a particular named "
"destination embedded in the document."
msgstr ""
"&PDF;-dokumentide puhul võib nime määrata kujul <replaceable>dokumendi_nimi</"
"replaceable>#<replaceable>nimega_sihtkoht</replaceable>, kus "
"<replaceable>nimega_sihtkoht</replaceable> on konkreetne dokumenti põimitud "
"nimega sihtkoht."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Command Line Options"
msgstr "Muud käsurea võtmed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1326
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following command line help options are available"
msgstr "Kasutada saab järgmisi käsurea abivõtmeid"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>okular</command> <option>-p --page <replaceable>number</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>okular</command> <option>-p --page <replaceable>number</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open a page with a given number in the document. Also available through "
"<userinput><command>okular</command> <option>-p <replaceable>number</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Avab dokumendis määratud numbriga lehekülje. Sama tulemuse annab "
"<userinput><command>okular</command> <option>-p <replaceable>number</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1336
#, no-c-format
