"<action>Show a preview</action> of how the currently displayed document "
"would be printed with the default options."
msgstr ""
"<action>Näitab</action>, milline on parajasti avatud dokumendi väljatrükk "
"vaikevalikute korral."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1568
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
