"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Activates</action> the Presentation Mode. For more information, see "
"the section about <link linkend=\"presentationMode\">Presentation Mode</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Aktiveerib</action> esitlusrežiimi. Täpsemalt räägib sellest osa "
"<link linkend=\"presentationMode\">Esitlusrežiim</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1780
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
#| "keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Full Screen "
#| "Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Full Screen Mode</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Täisekraanirežiim</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1787
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<action>Enables the full screen mode</action>. Note that full screen mode "
#| "is different from <link linkend=\"presentationMode\">presentation mode</"
#| "link> insofar as the only peculiarity of full screen mode is that it "
#| "hides the window decorations, the menubar and the toolbar."
msgid ""
"<action>Enables the full screen mode</action>. Note that full screen mode is "
"different from presentation mode insofar as the only peculiarity of full "
"screen mode is that it hides the window decorations, the menubar and the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<action>Lülitab sisse</action> täisekraanirežiimi. Pane tähele, et see "
"erineb <link linkend=\"presentationMode\">esitlusrežiimist</link> - "
"täisekraanirežiim erineb tavalisest ainult selle poolest, et näha pole "
"aknadekoratsioone, menüüriba ja tööriistariba."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1795
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom In</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Suurenda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1802
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Increase the magnification</action> of the document view."
msgstr "<action>Suurendab</action> dokumendi vaadet."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom Out</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vähenda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1815
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Decrease the magnification</action> of the document view."
msgstr "<action>Vähendab</action> dokumendi vaadet."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1820
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Auto Fit</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom to 100%</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Automaatne mahutamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1826
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<action>Goes to the previous occurrence of the search string</action> in "
#| "the document."
msgid ""
"<action>Zoom the document image to the actual size</action> as prescribed by "
"the document parameters."
msgstr "<action>Liigub otsingumõiste eelmisele asukohale</action> dokumendis."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1831
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fit Width</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mahuta laiusele</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Change the magnification</action> of the document view to a value "
"that makes the pages' width equal to the document view's width."
msgstr ""
"<action>Muudab</action> dokumendi suurendust, et see täidaks laiuti kogu "
"vaate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1844
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fit Page</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mahuta leheküljele</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Change the magnification</action> of the document view to a value "
"that makes at least one whole page visible."
msgstr ""
"<action>Muudab</action> dokumendi suurendust, et see täidaks kogu vaate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1856
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Auto Fit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Automaatne mahutamine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Change the magnification</action> of the document view to a value "
"that, depending on the size relation between the page and the view area, "
"automatically either makes the pages' width equal to the document view's "
"width (like fit-width), the pages' height equal to the document view's "
"height (like fit-height), or the whole page visible (like fit-page)."
msgstr ""
"<action>Suurenduse muutmine</action> dokumendivaates selliseks, et sõltuvalt "
"lehekülje ja vaateala suuruse suhtes lehekülje laius oleks võrdne "
"dokumendivaate laiusega (nagu laiusele mahutamise korral), lehekülje kõrgus "
"oleks võrdne dokumendivaate kõrgusega (nagu kõrgusele mahutamise korral) või "
"kogu lehekülg oleks nähtaval (nagu lehekülje mahutamise korral)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1868
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Vaaterežiim</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1874
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu makes you choose the view mode for the pages. The possible "
"options are: <guimenuitem>Single Page</guimenuitem> (only one page per row), "
"<guimenuitem>Facing Pages</guimenuitem> (two pages per row, in a book "
"style), <guimenuitem>Facing Pages (Center First Page)</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Overview</guimenuitem> (the number of columns is the one "
"specified in the <link linkend=\"configure\">&okular; settings</link>)."
msgstr ""
"See alammenüü võimaldab valida lehekülgede kuvamise režiimi. Valikud on "
"järgmised: <guimenuitem>Üksik</guimenuitem> (ainult üks lehekülg korraga), "
"<guimenuitem>Kõrvuti</guimenuitem> (kaks lehekülge kõrvuti nagu raamatus), "
"<guimenuitem>Kõrvutised leheküljed (esimene lehekülg tsentreeritakse)</"
"guimenuitem> ja <guimenuitem>Ülevaade</guimenuitem> (veergude arvu saab "
"määrata <link linkend=\"configure\">&okular;i seadistustes</link>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, you can enable the <guimenuitem>Continuous</guimenuitem> mode. "
"In continuous mode, all pages of the document are shown, and you can "
"smoothly scroll through them. Otherwise, only one page (or one row of pages) "
"is shown at a time."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1888
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Orientation</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Orientatsioon</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu allows you to <action>changes the orientation</action> of the "
"pages of the document."
msgstr ""
"See alammenüü võimaldab <action>muuta</action> dokumendi lehekülgede "
"orientatsiooni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1899
#, no-c-format
msgid "The rotation is applied to the orientation of every page."
msgstr "Pööramist rakendatakse iga lehekülje orientatsioonile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select <guimenuitem>Original Orientation</guimenuitem> to restore "
"the orientation of the document, discarding all the rotations applied "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Dokumendi orientatsiooni taastamiseks võib valida <guimenuitem>Algne "
"orientatsioon</guimenuitem>, mis tühistab kõik käsitsi tehtud pööramised."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1912
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Trim View</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Vaate kärpimine</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1918
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu allows you to remove the white border of pages when viewing "
"pages (<guimenuitem>Trim Margins</guimenuitem> item) or trim viewport to "
"selection (<guimenuitem>Trim To Selection</guimenuitem> item)."
msgstr ""
"Selle alammenüü abiga saab lehti vaadates eemaldada neilt valge piirde "
"(<guimenuitem>Kärbi veeriseid</guimenuitem>) või kärpida vaadet valikule "
"(<guimenuitem>Kärbi valikule</guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>trim to selection</quote> mode allows you to draw a selection "
"over the rendered page in order to define a visible bounding box to be "
"applied to <emphasis>all pages</emphasis> in the document. Selecting a small "
"trim bounding box enforces minimum dimensions size (20% as a percentage of "
"total page size)."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Valikule kärpimine</quote> lubab märkida nähtaval lehel valiku, mille "
"alusel kärbitakse samamoodi dokumendi <emphasis>kõiki</emphasis> lehekülgi. "
"Väikese kärpekasti märkimine kehtestab minimaalse suuruse (20% lehekülje "
"kogusuurusest)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>trim margins</quote> mode is persistent across &okular; restarts. "
"The <quote>trim to selection</quote> mode is forgotten across &okular; "
"restarts."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Veeriste kärpimine</quote> jäetakse meelde ka &okular;i "
"taaskäivituste ajaks. <quote>Valikule kärpimine</quote> kehtib aga vaid "
"&okular;i seansi ajal ja taaskäivituse järel sellega ei arvestata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you switch &okular; from <quote>trim margins</quote> mode to "
"<quote>trim to selection</quote> mode, the view jumps out of <quote>trim "
"margins</quote> mode for the bounding box selection interaction."
msgstr ""
"Kui lülitada &okular; <quote>veeriste kärpimiselt</quote> <quote>valikule "
"kärpimise</quote> peale, väljub vaade <quote>veeriste kärpimise</quote> "
"režiimist ning annab kohe võimaluse määrata vaate piiramise ala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The trim mode can be deactivated by selecting the same menu item that "
"activates it once again."
msgstr ""
"Kärpimisrežiimi saab välja lülitada sama menüükäsku valides, millega see "
"sisse lülitati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1937
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show/Hide Forms</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Näita vorme / Peida vormid</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show or hides the display</action> of the form fields of the "
"document."
msgstr "<action>Näitab või peidab</action> dokumendi vormivälju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1948
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu item is active only if the current document has form fields."
msgstr ""
"Seda alammenüüd saab kasutada ainult juhul, kui antud dokumendis on "
"vormiväljad."

